In its report published in Brussels, the European Commission, the Scientific Committee on New and Newly-identified Health Risks (SCENIHR), informed of the fact that it had issued an opinion today.
"The opinion shows that 5-10 percent of those who listen to their portable music player for more than an hour a day for five years can suffer permanent hearing loss" – can be read in the explanation.
